        "body": "Bumps the swift-deps group with 1 update in the /apps/swabble directory: [github.com/apple/swift-testing](https://github.com/apple/swift-testing).\n\nUpdates `github.com/apple/swift-testing` from 6.3.1 to 6.3.2\n<details>\n<summary>Release notes</summary>\n<p><em>Sourced from <a href=\"https://github.com/apple/swift-testing/releases\">github.com/apple/swift-testing's releases</a>.</em></p>\n<blockquote>\n<h2>Swift 6.3.2 Release</h2>\n<h2>What's Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>[6.3.2] Fully-qualify reference to 'Comment' type in #expect expansion when comment argument isn't a string literal by <a href=\"https://github.com/stmontgomery\"><code>@​stmontgomery</code></a> in <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/swiftlang/swift-testing/pull/1652\">swiftlang/swift-testing#1652</a></li>\n<li>[6.3.2] Diagnose the use of a generic clause on <code>@Test</code>, <code>@Suite</code>, and <code>@Tag</code>. by <a href=\"https://github.com/grynspan\"><code>@​grynspan</code></a> in <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/swiftlang/swift-testing/pull/1653\">swiftlang/swift-testing#1653</a></li>\n<li>Bump the Swift version to 6.3.2 by <a href=\"https://github.com/shahmishal\"><code>@​shahmishal</code></a> in <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/swiftlang/swift-testing/pull/1661\">swiftlang/swift-testing#1661</a></li>\n<li>[6.3.2] Fix off-by-one error trimming barrier sequences from exit test output streams. by <a href=\"https://github.com/grynspan\"><code>@​grynspan</code></a> in <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/swiftlang/swift-testing/pull/1695\">swiftlang/swift-testing#1695</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href=\"https://github.com/swiftlang/swift-testing/compare/swift-6.3.1-RELEASE...swift-6.3.2-RELEASE\">https://github.com/swiftlang/swift-testing/compare/swift-6.3.1-RELEASE...swift-6.3.2-RELEASE</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Commits</summary>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/swiftlang/swift-testing/commit/70eff